I. What is Quercus ?
-----------------------------------------------------
Quercus is Caucho Technologyâ€™s fast, open-source, 100% Java implementation of the PHP language.


II. Why a fork ?
-----------------------------------------------------
Clever Cloud has forked the Quercus project, formerly maintained by Caucho, to have a best response for issues and features requests.
You can find the Git-port of Caucho SVN in the branch 'caucho' : http://github.com/CleverCloud/Quercus/tree/caucho


